N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4023.7 - Result of each race to be reported

State Regulations

The placing judge or judges shall, at the close of each
day's racing, sign and send a report of the result of each race to the stewards
and the commission. Notes
